OL,6,B     ChunkyText Telesoftware Index     
OL,7,B```````````````````````````````````````
OL,8,BThis section of ChunkyText demonstrates
OL,9,Bthe telesoftware download functionality
OL,10,Bof the Volex TTX2000S teletext adapter 
OL,11,Bfor the Sinclair ZX Spectrum.          
OL,12,B                                       
OL,13,BTo download a program press 'T' and key
OL,14,Bin a page number from the list below.  
OL,15,B                                       
